phase-review: feat/hy2-live-users — Ф2 iter2: GHCR publish workflow
change: add .github/workflows/ghcr.yml — builds the HyPanel image (linux/amd64) and
  pushes to ghcr.io/by-sonic/hypanel:{latest,sha} on push to main, via built-in
  GITHUB_TOKEN (packages:write), gha build cache. Enables install.sh fast `docker pull`
  instead of build-from-source on small VPS. Pushes the already-VPS-verified installer
  commit d85da0c to main in the same push.
review: SELF-REVIEW — CI workflow config; the authoritative test is the Action run
